            "notes": [
                "Total Required Credits for the Program: 120 s.h. Students must earn a grade of at least a C minus in each course under Core Requirements and Sequences. A C minus or above is required in all prerequisites to other courses. Students must maintain a 2.5 GPA in their 40 credits of the major, and a 2.0 overall GPA to graduate with a BA in Sports Communication & Media. Transfer courses of 300 level or above that correlate with Rowanâ€™s courses will be accepted in the major. Students may earn up to 9 credits in internships. Any other internships can be taken on their own, but not for credit. Coordinator Dr. Emil Steiner 6 East High Street, Glassboro, NJ 856.256.4049 steiner@rowan.edu",
